Dear [First Name]  

 
 
We have a Gauthami Sr. SQL Server Developer. She is in NJ. She can Relocate Anywhere in U.S.A. She is available for the Project 
Immediately.
 
SUMMARY:
 
v  7 Years of IT experience in System Analysis, Design, Development, deployment and testing of custom applications using MS SQL SERVER 2008/2005/2000 with various business domains like Health Care, Insurance and Financial Banking
v  Involved in designing Fact tables and Dimension tables, Physical and Logical data models using ERWIN tool.
v  Extensive experience with SQL Server and T-SQL in creating tables, views, indexes, user profiles, relational database models, data dictionary, Stored Procedures, and user defined functions and triggers.
v  Good knowledge of Normalization/De-normalization, data design methodology and building Referential Integrity for the relational Database Model implementing as per business requirement.
v  Experience in High Level Design of ETL Packages for integrating data using OLE DB connection from heterogeneous sources (Excel, CSV, Oracle, flat file, Text Format Data) by using multiple transformations
v  High Expertise in ETL - Data Extraction, Transformation, Loading with Oracle, Access and SQL Server using DTS/SSIS. Experience in Import and Export Wizard, Package Installation, and SSIS Package Designer.
v  Experience in working with SSIS for creating packages to transform data from different OLEDB Provider like Flat File, Excel, and Oracle and Automate the ETL.
v  Expertise in Extract, Transform and Load (ETL) using SSIS and various tools including Bulk insert, BCP, Import Export data, DTS packages and SQL Server Integration Analyzed, designed and developed for a Data Warehousing and Data Migrations.
v   Experience in providing Logging, Error handling by using Event Handler, and Custom Logging for SSIS Packages
v  Experience with .NET framework using ASP.NET, C#, XML and ADO.NET database connectivity
v  Experience in creating OLAP Data marts using SQL Server Analysis Server (SSAS).
v  Created/modified a variety of parameterized, drill down, click through, chart, matrix, sub reports using SSRS 2005/2008 using data from a variety of sources. 
v  Experienced in generating on-demand (ad-hoc reports) for business analysis or management decision using SQL Server Reporting Services and Crystal Reports..
v  Experience in Creating Dynamic Grouping Matrix and Tabular Reports using SSRS.
v  Deployed SSRS Reports on web portals and Microsoft SharePoint Server 2010.
v  Strong knowledge of Data Warehousing methodologies and concepts, including star schemas, snowflakes, ETL processes, dimensional modeling and reporting tools.
v  Good team player, strong interpersonal and communication skills combined with self-motivation.
 TECHNICAL SKILLS:
 
SQL Server Tools                  : Enterprise Manager, Profiler, Query Analyzer, Export & Import                        
                                                           (DTS), SSIS, SSRS, SSAS.
RDBMS                                  : MS SQL Server 2000/2005/2008, MS Access, Excel
Data Modeling                       : Erwin, MS VISIO 
ETL                                                    : DTS, SSIS
Programming Languages      : T-SQL, VB scripts, C, C++, PL/SQL
Application Development   : HTML, XML, CSS, .NET, C#, VB.NET
IT Processes                          : Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC), Project Management
Productivity Applications    : MS Word, MS Excel, MS Access, MS Project.
Operating Systems               : Windows 2000/NT 4.0, Windows 2003 Advanced Server/  
                                                             Windows 95/98/200/XP-pro
Reporting Tools                     :  SSRS, Crystal Reports
 
 
